Functions I've used over and over again converted to an include instead of copy pasting between scripts and trying to keep all versions up to date. Feel free to use this however.

INVENTORY MANAGEMENT SECTION

    Available Functions: is_pack_open, get_pack_slot_name, is_top_slot_pack, select_first_item_in_inventory
	
MOVEMENT MANAGEMENT SECTION
    Available Functions: travel_to_remote_zone(w/ Optional Location and Heading)